div.p:
'Zounds, sir, you're
robb'd; for shame, put on
your gown;

Be it as you shall
privately determine, Either
for her stay or going:

knit to thy deserving with
cables of perdurable
toughness;

if thou canst cuckold him,
thou dost thyself a
pleasure,

either by speaking too
loud, or tainting his
discipline;

to your desires by the
means I shall then have to
prefer them;

Our general cast us thus
early for the love of his
Desdemona;

O, they are our friends;
but one cup: I'll drink
for you.

He'll drink you, with
facility, your Dane
dead drunk;

I remember a mass of
things, but nothing
distinctly;

of her parts and graces:
confess yourself freely
to her;

I have been to-night
exceedingly well
cudgelled;

Thou know'st we work by
wit, and not by
witchcraft;

His bed shall seem a
school, his board a
shrift;

With Cassio's suit:
therefore be merry,
Cassio;

Who steals my purse steals
trash; 'tis something,
nothing;

No, Iago; I'll see before
I doubt; when I doubt,
prove;

He thought 'twas
witchcraft-- but I am much
to blame;

I slept the next night
well, fed well, was free
and merry;

By the world, I think my
wife be honest and think
she is not;

Ay, let her rot, and
perish, and be damned
to-night;

I'll give over my suit and
repent my unlawful
solicitation;

Forth of mine heart those
charms, thine eyes, are
blotted;
